f the sport of wrestling.\r\nUnited World Wrestling desire is to elevate the sport of wrestling, stakeholders and knowledge to create tailored programmes relevant for the global wrestling family.\r\nAll nations will have the opportunity to benefit from these programme pathways as they are progressively developed.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1525441885993{background-color: #ffffff !important;}\"][vc_column][vc_separator color=\"custom\" border_width=\"10\" el_class=\"c-brand--corporate\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1525442649739{background-color: #ffffff !important;}\"][vc_column width=\"5/6\" css=\".vc_custom_1525441912979{background-color: #ffffff !important;}\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 class=\"mkdf-st-title\">THE DEVELOPMENT DEPARTMENT</h2>\r\nIs responsible for providing support to the national federations through a number of programs in close collaboration with the respective continental council.\r\nTogether with the Continental Councils resources are allocated towards these programs for those countries who need assistance most.\r\nUWW allocates more than 50% of income from the Olympic Games to the development of wrestling worldwide.[/vc_column_text][vc_separator color=\"custom\" border_width=\"10\" el_class=\"c-brand--corporate\"][team_carousel ids=\"1276, 1307, 1277, 1279, 1278, 1280\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][vc_single_image image=\"1158\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"center\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_empty_space][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_cta h2=\"United World Wrestling Coach Pathway\" h4=\"Rationale and Proposal of Level 1, 2, 3 Coaches Courses\" txt_align=\"center\" add_button=\"bottom\" btn_title=\"Read now!\" btn_color=\"warning\" btn_align=\"center\" btn_i_icon_fontawesome=\"fa fa-file-pdf-o\" btn_css_animation=\"none\" css_animation=\"none\" btn_add_icon=\"true\" btn_link=\